## Install

Install it directly from a terminal using the command:

\`\`\`shell
apm install ${tempus_theme_name_slug_full}-syntax
\`\`\`

Alternatively, search for \`${tempus_theme_name_slug_full}-syntax\` in Settings > Install > Themes. 

